The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on topic modeling using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also evaluates the proposed approach using information retrieval (IR) metrics, which suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of pre-trained embeddings and transfer learning techniques indicates that it could be relevant to cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of neural networks in the proposed approach suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.DL (Deep Learning).
